summary: An ominus looking tower has appeared in Skyrim *Work in Progress*
descriptionHtml:
From the makers of Jaggarsfeld.
<br />
<br />A dark tower ripped from the Soul Cairn has appeared in Skyrim.

This is a Work in Progress so don't expect much at the moment, but if you know of the features in Jaggarsfeld then you'll know what to expect here...if all goes according to plan.
author: DarthXile and TechAngel85
